Order Details 评价完成 Upload a real image, the first step to forge your personal brand When posting skills, you are required to upload a real and clear image as the head portrait which is the key identification of your personal brand in House Management. In this way, you can leave clients a good expression and attract more attention on you. Upload photos to the album for credibility enhancement You are recommended to upload 1 to 3 photos to show your skills and service. A Candid shot with sunny smile is another good choice. All the photos will make you more professional and real, which will boost clients\' trust on you. Upload ID card/skill certificates to prove the authenticity and skill level When the uploading work is done, endorsement marks will be with your which show your real identification and skill level. Clients prefer to select Pros with endorsement marks. At the same time, we will preferentially recommend more high-quality orders to endorsed Pros. Detailed service description is the key to get orders When posting skills, detailed service description, real work and education experiences are helpful for clients to know about your background, service category and skills level, which have an important impact on his/her decision. More competitive price, more clients\' attention When you fill in the quote, we recommend that on the premise of same quality of service, lower price is more attractive to clients, which will bring more probability to get the order. Grab orders actively for more chance to take an order After an order is posted, please send quote as soon as possible if you want to get the order . The more order invitations you respond to, the more opportunities you will get the order and complete the task finally. Pay more attention to order notifications for grabbing the order immediately After your skills are posted, notifications will be sent to you if the order is a good fit. As there are many clients want to get service as soon as possible, you should keep an eye on notifications so as to snatch online orders in time. Showing your strength through clients\' reviews and ratings Don\'t forget to ask clients to review and rate when service is done. More reviews and higher rating can attract more clients. In the meantime, we will preferentially recommend more high-quality clients to you. Higher scores, more orders Responding to invitation frequently, finishing the task and getting nice reviews are critical to raise Pros\' credit rating. Statistics show that clients prefer to select Pros with higher credit rating. Higher scores mean you are more active in the platform and more credible. Furthermore, Pros with higher credit rating have the priority to be recommended to get good orders. More skills, more money According to the category we set, you can post different kind of skills combining with your own expertise for increasing the income. Statistics show that more skills are posted, the income will be multiplied. House Management help you forge personal service brand We commit ourselves to assisting every single Pro to forge personal service brand.
